                            <li>Add a clear description</li>
                            <li>Submit for community review</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="help-item">
                        <h3>üìä Understanding Stats</h3>
                        <p>The <strong>Stats</strong> page shows community metrics and popular content.</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>View top-voted content</li>
                            <li>See community growth trends</li>
                            <li>Check platform statistics</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="help-item">
                        <h3>üè† Navigation</h3>
                        <p>Use the main navigation to explore different sections:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>Home</strong> - Overview and featured content</li>
                            <li><strong>Feed</strong> - Latest community submissions</li>
                            <li><strong>Submit</strong> - Add new content</li>
                            <li><strong>Stats</strong> - Community metrics</li>
